{
  "eyebrow": "Agent Logic Map",
  "title": "Day 2 · 真实模型 + tool_use / tool_result",
  "subtitle": "这张图只放 Day 2 的核心变化：真实 Provider、Anthropic content blocks，以及 tool_result 回到下一轮 user message。",
  "diagrams": [
    {
      "id": "main-loop",
      "label": "Main loop",
      "title": "真实模型的 tool calling 闭环",
      "summary": "从 user prompt 进入 messages，到 AnthropicProvider 返回 tool_use，再由 ToolRegistry 执行 system_date，最后把 tool_result 写回 messages 并让模型生成 final text。",
      "defaultActiveNodeId": "provider",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "cli",
          "kind": "runtime",
          "label": "CLI Runtime",
          "eyebrow": "entry",
          "body": "解析 prompt",
          "detail": "CLI Runtime 仍然只负责接住用户输入。Day 2 的变化不在 CLI，而在 provider 和 messages 协议形状。",
          "position": { "x": 0, "y": 80 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "messages",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "messages",
          "eyebrow": "context",
          "body": "role='user'",
          "detail": "messages 是发给 Messages API 的上下文。第一轮只有用户问题；工具执行后会追加 assistant tool_use 和 user tool_result。",
          "position": { "x": 300, "y": 80 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "provider",
          "kind": "model",
          "label": "AnthropicProvider",
          "eyebrow": "provider",
          "body": "messages.create(...)",
          "detail": "AnthropicProvider 只做协议适配：把 messages 和 tools schema 发到 Anthropic-compatible API，再把返回的 content blocks 翻译成内部 ModelResponse。它不执行工具。",
          "position": { "x": 600, "y": 80 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 210 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tool-use",
          "kind": "response",
          "label": "ModelResponse",
          "eyebrow": "tool_use",
          "body": "tool_call: system_date",
          "detail": "模型看到 system_date 的 input_schema，知道自己没有实时时钟，于是返回 tool_use content block。这里只是提议，不是执行。",
          "position": { "x": 900, "y": 80 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 210 }
        },
        {
          "id": "registry",
          "kind": "tool",
          "label": "ToolRegistry",
          "eyebrow": "harness",
          "body": "run system_date",
          "detail": "真正执行 system_date 的是 harness 里的 ToolRegistry。Day 2 仍然只做 registry lookup，权限检查会在 Day 5 加进来。",
          "position": { "x": 900, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 280, "y": 420 }
        },
        {
          "id": "tool-result",
          "kind": "response",
          "label": "ToolResult",
          "eyebrow": "observation",
          "body": "current datetime",
          "detail": "ToolResult 保存 system_date 返回的本机时间字符串。下一步不是写 role='tool'，而是打包进下一轮 user message 的 tool_result content block。",
          "position": { "x": 600, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 420 }
        },
        {
          "id": "stdout",
          "kind": "output",
          "label": "stdout",
          "eyebrow": "terminal",
          "body": "final answer",
          "detail": "第二次 complete(messages) 后，模型读到 tool_result，返回最终文本。CLI 打印 final，Agent Loop 结束。",
          "position": { "x": 0, "y": 320 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 630 }
        }
